Basic Chatbot
Description
This is a simple text-based chatbot built using Python and NLTK. The chatbot can respond to basic greetings, answer questions about itself, tell jokes and facts, provide basic sentiment analysis, and fetch weather updates.

Features:-
Responds to greetings and common questions
Provides simple jokes and fun facts
Performs basic sentiment analysis (detects positive or negative emotions)
Fetches weather updates for a given city (API integration required)
Simple conversation memory
